data.description:
Nestled in Goodyear, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home invites you to experience the epitome of comfort and style. The spacious living are bathed in natural light sets the stage for big family gatherings or entertaining friends. The four bedrooms provide comfort sanctuaries, each thoughtfully designed to create a sense of tranquility. The primary suite, with its ensuite bathroom, offers private escape for relaxation and rejuvenation.

Plus, get ready for non-stop excitement with live events at the Goodyear Ballpark throughout the year, including Major League Baseball Spring Training games, making every season a memorable one. Seize this golden opportunity to call this exceptional home yours and live in the heart of all that Goodyear has to offer!
